+    /// A pointer to the source slice DST.
+    source: T,
+    /// The length of the future left half of `source`.
+    ///
+    /// # Safety
+    ///
+    /// If `source` is a pointer to a slice DST, `l_len` is no greater than
+    /// `source`'s length.
